    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>- 创建账户仅需用户名，无需提供其他信息 -</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>行动迅速，出击有力</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你驾驶着强大的Xalium战斗坦克（XBT），通过WASD键操控移动。也可点击移动，但快速调整位置至关重要——XBT侧面承受的伤害更大，后方更甚。这使得站位成为命中目标的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >事实上，你必须每次击球都瞄准精准，因为每次击球都是技巧球！  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>虫群战场</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199180/extras/e5ee36e89d677f45744488d9c254c889.poster.avif?t=1757573482\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199180/extras/e5ee36e89d677f45744488d9c254c889.webm?t=1757573482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199180/extras/e5ee36e89d677f45744488d9c254c889.mp4?t=1757573482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每条战线每分钟涌现百余名小兵，战场上数千生灵涌动。无论是成群歼灭小兵、围攻英雄，还是压制防御塔，当你适应这种全新规模的战争后，再无其他MOBA游戏能与之比肩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>使命决定计划</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199180/extras/dada5670ddace35db3e7013a5e407717.poster.avif?t=1757573482\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199180/extras/dada5670ddace35db3e7013a5e407717.webm?t=1757573482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199180/extras/dada5670ddace35db3e7013a5e407717.mp4?t=1757573482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >罗特诺尔的街巷充斥着危险与财富。这座城市被分割为两半，每半区都由四个街区组成，分别由中立势力占据：警察、军队、海盗和索姆。你需决定与谁结盟，为他们执行任务，并获取能改变力量平衡的关键升级。待实力足够强大时，召集队伍挑战强大的螳螂——那叛变的XBT，争夺足以扭转战局的丰厚奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战术指挥官</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199180/extras/71dad59c784029f4c8b3b99ef23006aa.poster.avif?t=1757573482\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199180/extras/71dad59c784029f4c8b3b99ef23006aa.webm?t=1757573482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199180/extras/71dad59c784029f4c8b3b99ef23006aa.mp4?t=1757573482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从不断扩充的选项库中，选择与团队定位相契合的战斗坦克及驾驶员。每提升五级，即可通过改装强化技能。获取升级部件与装备，将坦克打造为契合你独特作战风格的专属战车。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>每道障碍皆是道路</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199180/extras/6d814ed71a89da0de70ebb1347d89ab9.poster.avif?t=1757573482\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199180/extras/6d814ed71a89da0de70ebb1347d89ab9.webm?t=1757573482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3199180/extras/6d814ed71a89da0de70ebb1347d89ab9.mp4?t=1757573482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你拥有摧毁一切阻碍的力量。在丛林中开辟新通道，从后方伏击敌人，或在他们以为胜券在握时发动后门突袭。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>阻止末日浩劫</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >整装待发，指挥官！虫群势不可挡，城市重塑权在你手，唯有真本事方能赢得胜利。集结你的团队，制定建设策略，在混乱中开辟道路，阻止末日降临！</p>",
